ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2012-13
PrecisAppointment of LAURENT CHARETTE as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Chad and the State of Eritrea, resident in Khartoum; MARCY GROSSMAN as Consul General of Canada in Denver, United States of America; TRUDY KERNIGHAN as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Sierra Leone, resident in Accra; THOMAS MacDONALD as Ambassador of Canada to the Sultanate of Oman, resident in Riyadh; IVAN ROBERTS as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Benin, resident in Ouagadougou; and MICHAEL SMALL as Ambassador of Canada to the Federated States of Micronesia, resident in Canberra.
